<img src="img/tina.png" alt="Tina Belcher" class="tina" title="Order Here">
<img src="img/register.png" alt="Cash Register" class="register" title="See All Burgers Sold">
<img src="img/generic-burger.png" alt="Burger" class="burger burger1 hidden" data-position="1">
<img src="img/chedda-burger.png" alt="Burger" class="burger burger2 hidden" data-position="2">
<img src="img/chive-burger.png" alt="Burger" class="burger burger3 hidden" data-position="3">
<img src="img/gordon-burger.png" alt="Burger" class="burger burger4 hidden" data-position="4">
<img src="img/olive-burger.png" alt="Burger" class="burger burger5 hidden" data-position="5">

<div class="burger-display hidden" id="burgerDisplay"></div>

<div class="modal" id="welcome">
  <img src="img/bob.png" alt="Bob" class="bob">
  <img src="img/speech-bubble.png" alt="Speech Bubble" class="speech-bob">
  <div class="welcome-text">
    <h1>Welcome to Bob's Burgers!</h1>
    <br>
    <h4>I'm Bob. I own this place along with my wife Linda and our kids. Feel free to order any burgers you want from my daughter Tina who is behind the counter.</h4>
    <br>
    <h4>Click on any burger on the counter to eat it.</h4>
    <br>
    <h4>If you want to see all the burgers that have ever been eaten here, go ahead and click on the cash register.</h4>
    <br>
    <h4>Well, I getter get back to the grill. Enjoy!</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal hidden" id="order-modal">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="img/order-modal.png" alt="menu" class="modal-order">
    <input type="text" id="burgerName" placeholder="BURGER NAME HERE">
    <button id="newBurger">ORDER</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal hidden" id="eaten-modal">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="img/eaten-modal.png" alt="menu" class="modal-order">
    <div class="list-container">
      <ul>
        {{#each burgers}}
          {{#if devoured}}
            <h2 data-id="{{id}}">{{burger_name}}</h2>
          {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>